INSERT INTO `wp_comments` VALUES (4,4,'John Williams','john@johnwilliams713.com','http://www.johnwilliams713.com/hula','208.49.232.191','2005-05-04 13:45:10','2005-05-04 17:45:10','Thanks for downloading my widget!',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X Mach-O; en-US; rv:1.7.7) Gecko/20050414 Firefox/1.0.3','',0,0),(5,4,'kellyjeanne','kelly@kellyjeanne.org','http://www.kellyjeanne.org','12.223.95.153','2005-05-05 10:26:22','2005-05-05 14:26:22','I LOVE her! ',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/412 (KHTML, like Gecko) Safari/412','',0,1),(6,4,'kellyjeanne','kelly@kellyjeanne.org','http://www.kellyjeanne.org','12.223.95.153','2005-05-05 12:32:52','2005-05-05 16:32:52','current widget count is up to 79!  yay! ',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/412 (KHTML, like Gecko) Safari/412','',0,1),(7,10,'kellyjeanne','kelly@kellyjeanne.org','http://www.kellyjeanne.org','12.223.95.153','2005-05-10 15:39:46','2005-05-10 19:39:46','I swear those fish are staring at me. ',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/412 (KHTML, like Gecko) Safari/412','',0,1),(8,6,'Mom/Jo','joanne.l.chambers@usps.gov','','56.0.143.23','2005-05-16 14:58:03','2005-05-16 18:58:03','Kelly,\r\nYour pottery is beautiful.  You\'ve got a talent for it.  And, I\'m not just saying this because I am Chad\'s mom!   Love you and I love your passion for it.  Keep it up!    Mom/Jo',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; NISSC; .NET CLR 1.0.3705)','',0,0),(9,6,'kellyjeanne','kelly@kellyjeanne.org','http://www.kellyjeanne.org','12.223.95.153','2005-05-16 22:49:13','2005-05-17 02:49:13','Thanks!  It helps to have such a supportive family behind me!  ',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/412 (KHTML, like Gecko) Safari/412','',0,1),(10,10,'Pete','p.steward@uea.ac.uk','','80.3.128.7','2005-05-17 11:37:38','2005-05-17 15:37:38','http://www.adb.org/Documents/Books/Live_Reef_Food_Fish_Trade/default.asp',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.7.7) Gecko/20050414 Firefox/1.0.3','',0,0),(11,10,'kellyjeanne','kelly@kellyjeanne.org','http://www.kellyjeanne.org','12.223.95.153','2005-05-19 10:07:15','2005-05-19 14:07:15','Thanks Pete, the link is interesting, however, I only buy tank raised freshwater fish, I don\'t have a reef tank or buy saltwater fish.  AND Freshewater Angels are from South America, not Southeast Asia. \r\n\r\n:)\r\n\r\n',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/412 (KHTML, like Gecko) Safari/412','',0,1),(25,13,'Yuga and Archana','vutti.yugandhar@ubs.com','','147.60.1.194','2005-07-07 00:48:28','2005-07-07 04:48:28','Hi Chad/Kelly..\r\nHope you both remember us - this is Yuga and Archana ( your ex-collegues at GE Bangalore).\r\nWe got married on 26th May 2005 (Atlast after waiting 4years for parents approval :-))\r\nI checked your site but cud not locate email address. Can u pls send one - so that i can send you our marriage snaps ?\r\n\r\nHave a great day..\r\nYuga/Archana',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; .NET CLR 1.0.3705; .NET CLR 1.1.4322)','',0,0),(20,12,'kellyjeanne','kelly@kellyjeanne.org','http://www.kellyjeanne.org','12.223.95.153','2005-06-14 10:24:18','2005-06-14 14:24:18','Well, I\'m sad to say that once again I\'ve unsuccesfully kept a delicate fish.  Mr. Punkrock turned up dead yesterday, Mrs. Punkrock appears to be missing this morning.  I guess I should wait a while before trying that again.  :(',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; PPC Mac OS X; en-us) AppleWebKit/412 (KHTML, like Gecko) Safari/412','',0,1),(34,13,'Martin','martinbarnett32@yahoo.com','http://spaghettilogic.blogspot.com/','24.24.101.173','2005-08-01 00:19:05','2005-08-01 04:19:05','Hello Kelly. Glad to hear that things are going well for you. We miss you at Otherlands. Things are changing there a little. Rearranging the cafe space, added coverage over the deck, a couple of fans outside. It is good to see you are back from your haitus. Oh, and get snails for your aquarium. Mine keep the water spotlessly clean, and provide a natural way to \'remove\' deceased fish. I had a fish die in the night awhile back, and by morning there was nothing but a few bones left...',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; SV1; .NET CLR 1.0.3705)','',0,0),(419,11,'free poker','pokermain@texas-holdem.ec','http://o3.indiatimes.com/free_poker','200.42.217.162','2006-02-05 00:05:46','2006-02-05 04:05:46','<a href=\"http://o3.indiatimes.com/free_poker\" title=\"free poker\">free poker</a> Nice :) Agree :)',0,'0','','',0,0),(420,11,'free poker','pokermain@texas-holdem.ec','http://o3.indiatimes.com/free_poker','213.130.18.214','2006-02-05 00:06:07','2006-02-05 04:06:07','<a href=\"http://o3.indiatimes.com/free_poker\" title=\"free poker\">free poker</a> Nice :) Agree :)',0,'0','','',0,0),(421,13,'texas holdem','main@freeonlinepoker.org','http://lucky7.to/texasholdem7/','200.69.119.202','2006-02-05 05:41:57','2006-02-05 09:41:57','<a href=\"http://lucky7.to/texasholdem7/\" title=\"texas holdem\">texas holdem</a> Nice :) Agree :)',0,'0','','',0,0),(422,13,'texas holdem','main@freeonlinepoker.org','http://lucky7.to/texasholdem7/','222.228.173.153','2006-02-05 05:42:18','2006-02-05 09:42:18','<a href=\"http://lucky7.to/texasholdem7/\" title=\"texas holdem\">texas holdem</a> Nice :) Agree :)',0,'0','','',0,0),(423,13,'texas holdem','main@freeonlinepoker.org','http://lucky7.to/texasholdem7/','203.145.148.20','2006-02-05 05:42:42','2006-02-05 09:42:42','<a href=\"http://lucky7.to/texasholdem7/\" title=\"texas holdem\">texas holdem</a> Nice :) Agree :)',0,'0','','',0,0),(424,9,'fantasy football','mike@online-poker.fr','http://z6q.us/','213.130.18.214','2006-02-05 15:06:24','2006-02-05 19:06:24','<a href=\"http://z6q.us/\" title=\"fantasy football\">fantasy football</a> Heh. How it goes? Buy it all. ASAP. Last discount in your live (AAAAA!!!!!). Take a re